  <header>
    <h1>Water Resources Engineering Specialization</h1>
    <p>Master the fundamentals of hydraulics, hydrology, water supply systems, and sustainable water management with comprehensive learning resources.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="wave-divider">
    <div class="wave"></div>
  </div>

  <section class="specialization-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Specialization Areas</h2>
    <div class="specialization-grid">
  
      <!-- Hydraulic Engineering -->
      <div class="specialization-card">
        <div class="specialization-title">
          <i class="fas fa-water"></i>
          Hydraulic Engineering
        </div>
        <p>Focus on the behavior and control of water flow in natural and engineered systems.</p>
        <br>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Open channel flow</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Hydraulic structures</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Pipe network analysis</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <div class="resources-section">
          <div class="resources-title">Learning Resources</div><br>
          <ul class="channel-list">
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/PracticalEngineering" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> Practical Engineering</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/TheEfficiency" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> The Efficiency</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.asce.org/communities/institutes-and-technical-groups/environmental-and-water-resources-institute" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-book"></i> ASCE EWRI Resources</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Hydrology -->
      <div class="specialization-card">
        <div class="specialization-title">
          <i class="fas fa-cloud-rain"></i>
          Hydrology
        </div>
        <p>Study of water movement, distribution, and quality across the Earth's surface and atmosphere.</p>
        <br>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Rainfall-runoff modeling</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Flood forecasting</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Groundwater analysis</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <div class="resources-section">
          <div class="resources-title">Learning Resources</div><br>
          <ul class="channel-list">
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/@nptel" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> NPTEL Hydrology</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/USGSWaterResources" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> USGS Water Resources</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://water.usgs.gov/edu/" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-book"></i> USGS Water Science School</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Water Resources Management -->
      <div class="specialization-card">
        <div class="specialization-title">
          <i class="fas fa-tint-slash"></i>
          Water Resources Management
        </div>
        <p>Focus on sustainable planning, development, and management of water resources.</p>
        <br>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Water allocation</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Reservoir operations</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Drought management</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <div class="resources-section">
          <div class="resources-title">Learning Resources</div><br>
          <ul class="channel-list">
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/WorldBank" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> World Bank Water</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/UNWater" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> UN Water</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.iwra.org/resources/" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-globe"></i> IWRA Resources</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
  
    </div>
  </section>
  

  <!-- Projects section -->
  <section class="projects-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Industry Projects</h2>
    <div class="projects-grid">
      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-title">
          <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
          Flood Risk Management
        </div>
        <p>Design and implement flood protection systems and early warning networks for urban areas.</p>
