  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Core Concepts</h2>
    <div class="topics-grid">
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Fluid Mechanics</div>
        <p>Understand the principles of fluid statics, dynamics, and the behavior of water in various conditions.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.efluids.com/efluids/pages/edu_resources.htm" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Open Channel Hydraulics</div>
        <p>Master the fundamentals of flow in rivers, channels, and other open conduits.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.hec.usace.army.mil/software/hec-ras/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Hydrologic Processes</div>
        <p>Learn about precipitation, infiltration, evapotranspiration, and runoff processes.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://water.usgs.gov/edu/watercycle.html" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="topics-grid">
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Groundwater Hydrology</div>
        <p>Study subsurface water movement, aquifer properties, and well hydraulics.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://water.usgs.gov/ogw/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Hydraulic Structures</div>
        <p>Understand design principles for dams, weirs, spillways, and other water control structures.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.usbr.gov/tsc/techreferences/mands/mands-pdfs/HydraulicStructures.pdf" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Water Supply Systems</div>
        <p>Learn about water treatment, distribution networks, and system design principles.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.awwa.org/Resources-Tools/Resource-Topics/Distribution-Systems" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Stormwater Management</div>
        <p>Study urban drainage systems, detention facilities, and low impact development.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.epa.gov/npdes/stormwater-management-practices" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">River Engineering</div>
        <p>Explore river mechanics, sediment transport, and river restoration techniques.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.usace.army.mil/Missions/Civil-Works/Project-Planning/nfpc/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Coastal Engineering</div>
        <p>Master principles of coastal processes, shoreline protection, and harbor design.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.coastal.edu/coastal/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Water Resources Planning</div>
        <p>Learn techniques for integrated water resources management and planning.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.iwra.org/iwrm/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Hydropower Engineering</div>
        <p>Study design and operation of hydroelectric facilities and energy production.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.energy.gov/eere/water/hydropower-basics" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Irrigation Systems</div>
        <p>Understand agricultural water management, irrigation methods, and efficiency.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.irrigation.org/IA/Resources/Technical-Resources/IA/Resources/Technical-Resources.aspx" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Water Quality Modeling</div>
        <p>Explore contaminant transport, water quality assessment, and pollution control.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.epa.gov/ceam/surface-water-quality-modeling" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Climate Change Impacts</div>
        <p>Learn about climate change effects on water resources and adaptation strategies.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.epa.gov/climate-impacts/climate-impacts-water-resources" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Watershed Management</div>
        <p>Study integrated approaches to managing land and water resources at watershed scale.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.epa.gov/hwp" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  

